replies.text:
@d69p-eix Off the top of my head... Hey Arnold and Rocket Power are two shows I remember that warned us against worshipping celebrities. I'm sure there's more I'm forgetting.

With Hey Arnold, there was an episode where Eugene is obsessed with a TV super hero based on Arnold Schwarzenegger. For Rocket Power, Otto was obsessed with the star of his favorite movie.

Oh, and there was an episode of Drake & Josh where Josh got to know some bratty kid movie star.
